doctype html
html
    head
        title About Us | ReShare
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="/style.css")
    body
        .wrapper
            include ./includes/nav.pug

            //- 1. High-Impact Hero Section
            section.about-hero
                .container
                    span.hero-badge Our Mission
                    h1.page-title Sustainable Living, Simplified.
                    p.hero-text ReShare is a community-based web application designed to reduce household waste and promote sustainable living by connecting people within local communities.

            //- 2. The Core Philosophy (The "Heart" of the text)
            section.about-philosophy
                .container
                    .philosophy-card
                        h2 Beyond Second-Hand Selling
                        p The platform allows users to list unwanted household items such as furniture, clothing, kitchenware, and electronics, making them available for others nearby to claim completely free of charge. 
                        p.highlight Unlike second-hand selling platforms, ReShare removes the financial element entirely—the focus is purely on reuse, redistribution, and keeping usable items out of landfill.
                        blockquote "One person's unwanted item becomes another person's useful one."

            //- 3. How It Works Grid
            section.about-how
                .container
                    h2.section-title How the Community Works
                    .listings-grid
                        .item-card.about-step
                            .pill-icon 🔍
                            h3 Browse & Filter
                            p Users can browse available listings in their area, filter by category, and request items directly through the platform's built-in messaging system.
                        
                        .item-card.about-step
                            .pill-icon 🤝
                            h3 Connect & Collect
                            p Once a claim is made, the two parties arrange collection between themselves, keeping the process straightforward and community-driven.
                        
                        .item-card.about-step
                            .pill-icon 🌿
                            h3 Think Twice
                            p ReShare aims to make sustainable habits easy and practical for everyday life rather than something that requires extra effort or cost.

            //- 4. Accessibility Statement (Footer of the page)
            section.about-accessibility
                .container
                    .access-box
                        p ReShare is built with accessibility and simplicity in mind, ensuring that anyone regardless of technical ability can register, browse, and participate.